gurmukhi: ਅਦ੍ਵੈ ਸਰੂਪ ਅਦ??ਿਯ ਅਮਰ ਅਭਿਬੰਦਤ ਸੁਰ ਨਰ ਅਸੁਰ ||੫||੩੬||
transliteration: Advai Saroopadviya Amar Abhibandat Sur Nar Asur||5||36||
translation: He is Non-dual Entity, Unique, Immortal and is deeply abored by gods, men and demons.5.36.

gurmukhi: ਕੁਲ ਕਲੰਕ ਕਰਿ ਹੀਨ ਕ੍ਰਿਪਾ ਸਾਗਰ ਕਰੁਣਾ ਕਰ ||
transliteration: Kul Kalank Kar(i) Heen Kridaa Saagad Karounaa Kar||
translation: He is the ocean and source of Mercy and remover of blemishes from all.

gurmukhi: ਕਰਣ ਕਾਰਣ ਸਮਰੱਥ ਕ੍ਰਿਪਾ ਕੀ ਸੂਰਤ ਕ੍ਰਿਤ ਧਰ ||
transliteration: Karan Kaaran Samratth Kridaa Kisoorat Krit Dhar||
translation: He is the cause of causes, Powerful, Merciful Entity and prop of creation.

gurmukhi: ਕਾਲ ਕਰਮ ਕਰ ਹੀਨ ਕ੍ਰਿਅਾ ਜਿਹ ਕੋੲਿ ਨ ਬੁੱਝੇ ||
transliteration: Kaal Karam Kar Heen Kriaa Jih Koe Na Bujjhe||
translation: He is the destroyer of the actions of death and none knows His doning.

gurmukhi: ਕਹਾ ਕਹੈ ਕਹ ਕਰੈ ਕਹਾ ਕਾਲਨ ਕੈ ਸੁੱਝੇ ||
transliteration: Kahaa Kahai Kah Darai Kahaa Kaalan Kai Sujjhe||
translation: What doth he say and do? What facts doth reveal Him?

gurmukhi: ਕੰਜਲਕ ਨੈਨ ਕੰਬੂ ਗ੍ਰੀਵਹਿ ਕਟਿ ਕੇਹਰਿ ਕੁੰਜਰ ਗਵਨ ||
transliteration: Kanjalak Nain Kanboo Greevah(i) Kattee Kehar(i) Kounjar Gadan||
translation: His eyes are like lotus, neck like conchshell, waist like lion and gait like elephant.

gurmukhi: ਕਦਲੀ ਕੁਰੰਕ ਕਰਪੂਰ ਗਤ ਬਿਨ ਅਕਾਲ ਦੂਜੋ ਕਵਨ ||੬||੩੭||
transliteration: Kadlikurank Karpoor Gad Bin Akaal Doojo Kavan||6||37||
translation: Legs like banana, swiftness like deer and fragrance like camphor, O non-temporal Lord! Who else can be without thee with such attributes?6.37.

gurmukhi: ਅਲਖ ਰੂਪ ਅਲੇਖ ਅਭੈ ਅਨਭੂਤ ਅਭੰਜਨ ||
transliteration: Alakh Roop Alekh Abhai Anbhoot Abhanjan||
translation: He is an Incomprehensible Entity, accountless, valueless, elementless and Unbreakable.

gurmukhi: ਅਾਦਿ ਪੁਰਖ ਅਬਿਕਾਰ ਅਜੈ ਅਨਗਾਧ ਅਗੰਜਨ ||
transliteration: Aadh Purakh Abikaar Ajai Anaddh Agadjan||
translation: He is the Primal Purusha, without vices, Unconquerable, Unfathomable and Invincible.
He is without vices, Unmalicious Entity, Unblemished and transcendent.
He is the Breaker of the Unbreakable, Indiscriminate, Elementless and Infrangible.

gurmukhi: ਸਾਹਾਨ ਸਾਹ ਸੁੰਦਰ ਸੁਮਤਿ ਬਡ ਸਰੂਪ ਬਡਵੈ ਬਖਤ ||
transliteration: Saahaan Saah Soundar Soumat(i) Bad Saroopbadvai Bakhat||
translation: He is the king of kings, Beautiful, of propitious intellect, of handsome countenance and Most Fortunate.

gurmukhi: ਕੋਟਿਕ ਪ੍ਰਤਾਪ ਭੂਅ ਭਾਨ ਜਿਮ ਤਪਤ ਤੇਜ ੲਿਸਥਿਤ ਤਖਤ ||੭||੩੮||
transliteration: Kotik Prataap Bhooa Bhaan Jim Tapat Tej Isthit Takhat||7||38||
translation: He is seated on His throne with the effulgence of millions of earthly suns.7.38.
